| gr13 = PS3：84%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps3/928790-final-fantasy-xiii/index.html|title=Final Fantasy XIII Reviews|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2011-08-06|language=en|archive-date=2009-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415231442/http://www.gamerankings.com/ps3/928790-final-fantasy-xiii/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><br />X360：82%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/950899-final-fantasy-xiii/index.html|title=Final Fantasy XIII Reviews|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2011-08-06|language=en|archive-date=2009-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422172754/http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/950899-final-fantasy-xiii/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
