}}

总体而言，最终幻想系列获得评论和商业上的成功，雖然各作品的成功程度有所不同。系列累计销量呈现稳定增长；系列1996年上半年全球销量突破1,000万套<ref name="cvg174">{{citation|title=Final Fantasy VII|magazine=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|issue=174|date=May 1996|pages=106-111}}</ref>，2003年8月時在全球售出4,500万套，2005年12月時為6,300万套，2008年7月時為8,500万套<ref name="85mil">{{cite press release |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/press-releases/38274/SONG-SUMMONER-The-Unsung-Heroes |title=Square Enix announces Song Summoner: The Unsung Heroes |publisher=Square Enix |accessdate=2011-08-02 |date=2008-07-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60eFGvWvv?url=http://www.mcvuk.com/press-releases/read/square-enix-announces-song-summoner-the-unsung-heroes |archivedate=2011-08-02 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2003/11082003/| title = Square Enix U.S.A. announces details for Final Fantasy XI| date = 2003-08-11| publisher = Square Enix| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eFaFkSD?url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2003/11082003/| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.square-enix.com/eu/en/whatsnew/oxmEN.pdf| title = (Official Xbox Magazine press release) Playable Beta Disc for Xbox 360 Console to be included with February 2006 Issue| format = PDF| date = 2005-12-19| publisher = Square Enix| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eFcdYVx?url=http://www.square-enix.com/eu/en/whatsnew/oxmEN.pdf| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。2011年6月，史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布系列销量超过一亿<ref name="100mil">{{cite web| url = http://gamasutra.com/view/news/35096/Final_Fantasy_Series_Hits_100M_Units_Shipped.php| title = Final Fantasy Series Hits 100M Units Shipped| publisher = UBM Tech| date = 2011-06-07| author = Mike Rose| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eGChfx6?url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/35096/Final_Fantasy_Series_Hits_100M_Units_Shipped.php| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>，2014年6月系列销量达到1.1亿<ref>{{cite web|title=CRYSTAL DYNAMICS UNVEILS RISE OF THE TOMB RAIDER|url=http://press.na.square-enix.com/releases/277/crystal-dynamics-unveils-rise-of-the-tomb-raider|publisher=Square Enix Co., Ltd.|accessdate=2014-06-26|language=en|date=2014-06-09|archive-date=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6QKd299Sd?url=http://press.na.square-enix.com/releases/277/crystal-dynamics-unveils-rise-of-the-tomb-raider|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终幻想是电子游戏产业中[[最畅销电子游戏系列列表|最畅销的系列]]之一；2007年1月在榜单排名第3，7月排名第4<ref name="Edge177" /><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.joystiq.com/2007/01/10/nintendo-holds-key-to-franchise-longevity-profitability/| title = Nintendo holds key to franchise longevity, profitability| author = James Ransom-Wiley| date = 2007-01-10| publisher = Joystiq| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eGExNRk?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/01/10/nintendo-holds-key-to-franchise-longevity-profitability/| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。截至2021年全系列出貨數與數位販售合計數量已逾1億6400萬份<ref name="164m"/>。

在2007年底时，當時世界畅销RPG排行的第七、八、九名分别为《最终幻想VII》、《最终幻想VIII》和《最终幻想X》<ref name="GWR08-RPG">{{cite book| last= |first= |editor= Craig Glenday| title= Guinness World Records Gamer's Edition 2008| url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0| series= [[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]]| date = 2008-03-11| publisher= Guinness|isbn= 978-1-904994-21-3| pages= [https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0/page/156 156]–167| chapter= Record Breaking Games: Role-Playing Games|language=en}}</ref>。初版《最终幻想VII》在全球銷量超过1330万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/idJP00093500_20210226_00820210226 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-02 |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220040958/https://www.reuters.com/article/idJP00093500_20210226_00820210226 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，为销量最高的最终幻想作品<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2005/05152005/| title = Square Enix Announces Release Date of Final Fantasy VII Advent Children| publisher = Square Enix| date = 2005-05-15| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eHFStEq?url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2005/05152005/| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《最终幻想VIII》1999年在北美首发两天内，登上美国的最畅销游戏週榜单，并占据首位三週多<ref name="charts">{{cite web| title = Final Fantasy VIII Tops Videogame Charts| date = 1999-10-05| url = http://psx.ign.com/articles/071/071008p1.html| publisher = IGN Entertainment| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eHW3TjD?url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/071/071008p1.html| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《最终幻想X》在日本仅预订销售就超过140万，创下當時游戏机RPG最快销售的记录<ref name="GWR08-RPG" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096716p1.html | title = Final Fantasy X Sells Like Crazy; World Not Shocked | publisher = IGN Entertainment | date = 2001-07-19 | accessdate = 2011-08-02 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eHjFM3z?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096716p1.html | archivedate = 2011-08-02 | language = en | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

MMORPG《最终幻想XI》在2006年3月每日有达20万的活跃用户<ref>{{cite web| author = Christopher Woodard| title = GDC: Creating a Global MMO: Balancing Cultures and Platforms in Final Fantasy XI| publisher = UBM Tech| date = 2006-03-24| url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/2635/gdc_all_about_ninetynine_nights_.php| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101207102248/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/2635/gdc_all_about_ninetynine_nights_.php| archivedate = 2010-12-07| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>，并在2007年7月达到50万消费用户<ref name="Edge177" />。《最终幻想XII》首周在日本售出170万<ref>{{cite web| author = David Jenkins| date = 2006-03-24| title = Japanese Sales Charts, Week Ending March 19| publisher = UBM Tech| url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=8671| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eIIhaVs?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=8671| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>，北美版发行首周也出货约150万套<ref>{{cite web| date = 2006-11-06| title = Square Enix Announces Record Shipment With Final Fantasy XII| publisher = Square Enix| url = http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2006/1106_1/| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60eIMMWY9?url=http://www.square-enix.com/na/company/press/2006/1106_1/| archivedate = 2011-08-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《最终幻想XIII》日本首发日出货100万套<ref name="GSUTRA1mil">{{cite web |author=Leigh Alexander |date=2009-12-18 |title=FFXIII Tops 1 Million Units Day One |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26571/FFXIII_Tops_1_Million_Units_Day_One.php |publisher=UBM Tech |accessdate=2009-12-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100510025507/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26571/FFXIII_Tops_1_Million_Units_Day_One.php |deadurl=no |archivedate=2010-05-10 |language=en }}</ref>。《最终幻想XIV：重生之境》和前作一样获得巨大成功，在游戏推出时出现服务器拥挤現象<ref name="Kotaku early">{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/early-final-fantasy-xiv-launch-goes-surprise-badly-1198833060 |title=Early Final Fantasy XIV Launch Goes (Surprise!) Badly |author=Plunkett, Luke |publisher=Kotaku |date=2013-08-25 |accessdate=2013-08-25 |language=en |archive-date=2013-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827150147/http://kotaku.com/early-final-fantasy-xiv-launch-goes-surprise-badly-1198833060 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其独立付费用户在两个月内超过100万名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/203676/Final_Fantasy_XIV_hits_15M_registrations_after_relaunch_woes.php|title=Final Fantasy XIV hits 1.5M registrations after relaunch woes|date=2013-10-30|work=Gamasutra|publisher=UBM Tech|accessdate=2013-10-31|language=en|author=Kris Ligman|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202202/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/203676/Final_Fantasy_XIV_hits_15M_registrations_after_relaunch_woes.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 评论反响 ===

系列在圖像和音樂品质上获评论称赞<ref name="Edge177" />。1996年《[[次世代_(杂志)|次世代]]》将其列为史上第17大游戏系列，并高度称赞其图像、音乐与剧情<ref name="NG1996">{{cite book |title=Next Generation|issue=21 |page=68 |publisher=Imagine Media |location=United States |issn= |date=1996-09|language=en}}</ref>。系列获2006年[[Walk_of_Game|Walk of Game]]的星章奖励，是首个获得星章的游戏系列（其他獲獎者皆为单个游戏而非系列）。WalkOfGame.com在评论中称系列寻求完美并敢于冒险革新<ref name="Walk">{{cite web| url = http://www.walkofgame.com/inductees/inductees.html| title = 2006 Walk of Game Inductees| publisher = Walk of Game| accessdate = 2011-08-02| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080702165340/http://www.walkofgame.com/inductees/inductees.html| archivedate = 2008-07-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]于2006年举办了最佳电子游戏系列竞赛，最终幻想位次[[塞尔达传说系列|塞尔达传说系列]]获得亚军<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/bse|title=Summer 2006: Best. Series. Ever|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2011-08-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606181323/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/bse|archivedate=2009-06-06|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。在2008年[[游戏_(零售商)|游戏集团股份有限公司]]举办的公众民意调查中，最终幻想获选成为最佳游戏系列，同时五部作品入选“史上最伟大游戏”<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.game.co.uk/lowdown.aspx?lid=9321| title = Greatest Games Results| publisher = The Game Group plc| year = 2008| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090206155411/http://www.game.co.uk/lowdown.aspx?lid=9321| archivedate = 2009-02-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

许多最终幻想游戏入选过各种最佳游戏列表。一些游戏登上多个[[IGN|IGN]]“最佳游戏”榜单<ref>{{cite web| url = http://top100.ign.com/2003/index.html| title = IGN's Top 100 Games| publisher = IGN Entertainment| year = 2003| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090222013658/http://top100.ign.com/2003/index.html| archivedate = 2009-02-22| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://top100.ign.com/2005/index.html| title = IGN's Top 100 Games| publisher = IGN Entertainment| year = 2005| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090227082124/http://top100.ign.com/2005/index.html| archivedate = 2009-02-27| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title = Top 99 Games of All Time: Readers' Pick| url = http://microsites.ign.com/kfc/top99games/| publisher = IGN Entertainment| year = 2005| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090218133535/http://microsites.ign.com/kfc/top99games/| archivedate = 2009-02-18| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://ps2.ign.com/articles/772/772296p3.html| title = The Top 25 PS2 Games of All Time| author = IGN PlayStation Team| publisher = IGN Entertainment| date = 2007-03-16| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090228201618/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/772/772296p3.html| archivedate = 2009-02-28| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/79|title=Top 100 PlayStation 2 Games|accessdate=2012-11-17|author=|date=|publisher=IGN Entertainment|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618075638/http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/79|archivedate=2013-06-18|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/24|title=Top 100 PlayStation 2 Games|accessdate=2012-11-17|author=|date=|publisher=IGN Entertainment|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618040824/http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/24|archivedate=2013-06-18|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。系列有11款游戏入选《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》2006年的“史上100大最喜爱的游戏”榜单，包括冠亚军《最终幻想X》和《最终幻想VII》在内，有四部游戏进入前十<ref name="Top100-famitsu">{{cite web| author = Colin Campbell| year = 2006| title = Japan Votes on All Time Top 100| url = http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100| publisher = Edge| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110806220418/http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。系列获得《[[吉尼斯世界纪录玩家版|吉尼斯世界纪录玩家版]]2008》的七项[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]，其中如“最多游戏的RPG系列”（13部本传、7部强化作品，以及32部衍生作品）、“最长开发周期”（《最终幻想XII》制作时间为5年）以及“单日内销售最快的游戏机RPG”（《最终幻想X》）<ref name="GWR08-RPG" /><ref name="guinness">{{cite web| url = http://gamers.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/300708_ffiv.aspx| title = Record Breaking Final Fantasy Series heads to The Record Breaking Nintendo DS| last = Parsons| first = Doug| date = 2008-07-30| publisher = Guinness World Records| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090602083919/http://gamers.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/300708_ffiv.aspx| archivedate = 2009-06-02| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。在《玩家版2009年版》的50款最佳游戏机游戏中，系列有两部游戏入选，分别为第八的《最终幻想XII》和第二十的《最终幻想VII》<ref>{{cite book| title = Guinness World Records 2009 Gamer's Edition| url = https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_x9q9| series= Guinness World Records| date = 2009-02-03| publisher= Guinness|isbn= 978-1-904994-45-9| pages= [https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_x9q9/page/190 190]–191| chapter= Top 50 Console Games|language=en}}</ref>。

系列也收到一些批评。IGN评论称，游戏使用選單戰鬥系统对许多人来说是一大缺点，这是“为什么他们不接触系列的重要原因”<ref name="IGN-Evo" />。网站还严厉批评系列战斗系统採用随机遇敌方式<ref name="IGNReview8">{{cite web| url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/153/153847p1.html| title=IGN: Final Fantasy VIII Review| publisher=IGN Entertainment| author=Jeff Lundigran| date=1999-09-10| accessdate=2011-08-06| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211123532/http://psx.ign.com/articles/153/153847p1.html| archivedate=2009-02-11| language=en| deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="IGNReview9">{{cite web| url = http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162190p1.html| title = IGN: Final Fantasy IX Review| publisher = IGN Entertainment| last = Smith| first = David| date = 2000-11-22| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090212170216/http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162190p1.html| archivedate = 2009-02-12| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。IGN又称，将系列电影与动画化的各种尝试，若非失败平庸，即不达游戏之水准<ref name="IGN-FF-Anime" />。《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》在2007年批评称，有大量不如前作的系列相关分支作品，它们的标题挂著“最终幻想”之名。评论还称，随着坂口博信的离开，系列或有逐渐陈腐之危<ref name="Edge177" />。

一些最终幻想作品获得額外關注；它們獲得的正负面评价皆有。《最终幻想VII》獲列《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》“史上最佳26个RPG”之榜首<ref>{{cite web | title=The 26 Best RPGs of the All Time | url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/218144/the-26-best-rpgs-page-4-of-4/ | publisher=GamePro | date=2008-11-05 | accessdate=2011-08-06 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806220746/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/218144/the-26-best-rpgs-page-4-of-4/ | archivedate=2011-08-06 | language=en | deadurl=yes }}</ref>，并成为GameFAQs 2004和2005年读者票选的“史上最佳游戏”<ref>{{cite web | title=Spring 2004: Best. Game. Ever | url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/c04spr | publisher=CBS Interactive | accessdate=2011-08-06 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090209040851/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/c04spr | archivedate=2009-02-09 | language=en | deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Fall 2005: 10-Year Anniversary Contest—The 10 Best Games Ever | url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 | publisher=CBS Interactive | accessdate=2011-08-06 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090316073741/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 | archivedate=2009-03-16 | language=en | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。尽管《最终幻想VII》很成功，但有时也有批评声称，游戏获得评价过高。游戏登上[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] 2003年“史上被高估游戏榜单”的第七位，而IGN上面也存在两种不同的评论声<ref>{{cite web| url = http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/september03/25overrated/| title = 25 Most Overrated Games of All Time| publisher = GameSpy| date = 2003-09| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090412074612/http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/september03/25overrated/| archivedate = 2009-04-12| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://retro.ign.com/articles/958/958466p1.html| title = Is Final Fantasy VII Overrated?| author = Levi Buchanan| publisher = IGN Entertainment| date = 2009-03-03| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090310095415/http://retro.ign.com/articles/958/958466p1.html?%3F| archivedate = 2009-03-10| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《[[地狱犬的挽歌_-最终幻想VII-|地狱犬的挽歌 -最终幻想VII-]]》发行首周出货39.2万，但评论得分则远低于其他最终幻想游戏<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.m-create.com/eng/e_ranking.html| title = Top 10 Weekly Software Sales| year = 2006| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060205034213/http://m-create.com/eng/e_ranking.html| archivedate = 2006-02-05| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/924449-dirge-of-cerberus-final-fantasy-vii/index.html| title = Dirge of Cerberus: Final Fantasy VII Reviews| publisher = CBS Interactive| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090625203933/http://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/924449-dirge-of-cerberus-final-fantasy-vii/index.html| archivedate = 2009-06-25| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/dirge-of-cerberus-final-fantasy-vii| title = Dirge of Cerberus: Final Fantasy VII Reviews| publisher = CBS Interactive| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110806221819/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/dirge-of-cerberus-final-fantasy-vii| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《Fami通》在游戏发行之后才发布评论，这种推延、负面的评论暗示杂志和史克威尔艾尼克斯间存在争议<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.1up.com/news/famitsu-digs-dirge-cerberus| publisher = IGN Entertainment Games| title = Famitsu Digs Into Dirge of Cerberus| author = Dan Dormer| date = 2006-02-08| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kHDatks?url=http://www.1up.com/news/famitsu-digs-dirge-cerberus| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。尽管《最终幻想：灵魂深处》在视觉效果获得称赞，但剧情却受到批评，电影亦被视为商業失敗<ref name="MC-Spirits" /><ref name="Edge177" /><ref name="FFMovie-RPGamer" /><ref>{{cite web| title = Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within| last = Ebert| first = Roger| url = http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20010711/REVIEWS/107110301/1023| publisher = RogerEbert.com| date = 2001-07-11| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090620013901/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20010711%2FREVIEWS%2F107110301%2F1023| archivedate = 2009-06-20| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[GameCube|GameCube]]的《最终幻想水晶编年史》总体获正面评分，但评论者称其用[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]当控制器乃一大缺点<ref name="IGN-StateOfRPG" /><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.1up.com/reviews/final-fantasy-crystal-chronicles| title = Reviews: FF: Crystal Chronicles| publisher = IGN Entertainment Games| date = 2000-01-01| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kHdFKRB?url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/final-fantasy-crystal-chronicles| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。因初版《最终幻想XIV》主要获得负面评价，前总裁和田洋一在东京的一场官方新闻发布会上正式道歉，称游戏所获评价是对品牌的“极大损害”<ref name="XIVapology">{{cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/comyby/|title=Square Enix CEO: Final Fantasy XIV Damaged FF Brand|author=Gantayat, Anoop|publisher=Andriasang.com|date=2011-09-27|accessdate=2013-12-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121225060037/http://andriasang.com/comyby/|deadurl=yes|archivedate=2012-12-25|language=en}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==

最终幻想系列——以及系列中的某些作品——開創推广许多当下游戏机RPG廣泛使用的要素<ref name="GS-FFHistory-Main" /><ref name="IGN-StateOfRPG" />。評論通常认为，系列首作是最具影响力的早期游戏机RPG之一，并在此类游戏的确立与推广中扮演重要角色。《[[勇者鬥惡龍_(遊戲)|勇者鬥惡龍]]》使用[[第一人称视角游戏|第一人称视角]]，单对单與怪物战斗；而《最终幻想》則引入常用的侧面鏡頭，一组玩家角色对一组敵方怪物的战斗方式<ref name="GS-FFHistory-Main" /><ref name="FF-Retro-1" /><ref name="IGN-StateOfRPG" />。系列引入早期的升级[[职业转换|转职]]系统<ref>{{cite web|title=Ranking the Final Fantasy Series|date=2009-12-29|publisher=IGN Entertainment|url=http://uk.ds.ign.com/articles/105/1057633p1.html|accessdate=2011-08-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60kKp3N1I?url=http://uk.ds.ign.com/articles/105/1057633p1.html|archivedate=2011-08-06|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|year=1989|title=Final Fantasy Explorer's Handbook (instruction manual)|publisher=Square|page=75|language=en}}</ref>，以及船、独木舟、飞空艇等多样的交通方式<ref name="GT-FFRetrospectiveII" />。系列还引入熟练度系统<ref name="IGN-FFII">{{cite web|url=http://psp.ign.com/articles/808/808182p1.html|title=Final Fantasy II Review|publisher=IGN Entertainment|date=2007-07-26|author=Jeremy Dunham|accessdate=2011-08-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60kKwXCYR?url=http://psp.ign.com/articles/808/808182p1.html|archivedate=2011-08-06|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，该系统之后被《[[沙加系列|-{zh-tw:復活邪神;zh-cn:沙加}-]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/romancingsagaminstrel/index.html|title=Romancing SaGa|author=Patrick Gann|publisher=RPGFan|accessdate=2011-08-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60kLLcH6i?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/reviews/romancingsagaminstrel/index.html|archivedate=2011-08-06|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>、《[[格兰蒂亚系列|-{zh-cn:格兰蒂亚;zh-tw:冒險奇譚}-]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162007p1.html|title=Grandia|publisher=IGN Entertainment|author=Francesca Reyes|date=1999-11-04|accessdate=2011-08-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60kLWfkHL?url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162007p1.html|archivedate=2011-08-06|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>和《[[上古卷轴系列|上古卷轴]]》等角色扮演游戏系列使用<ref name="IGN-FFII" />。《最终幻想III》引入职业系统，玩家可随时通过游戏的角色成长引擎转换角色职业，并可习得高级新职业和联合职业技能<ref name="FF3jobs">{{cite web |url=http://na.square-enix.com/ff3/ |title=Final Fantasy III |publisher=Na.square-enix.com |date= |accessdate=2011-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090627120205/http://na.square-enix.com/ff3/ |archivedate=2009-06-27 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。因《最终幻想IV》故事的戲劇性，着重强调角色的发展与人际关系，故媒体将作品視为RPG注重撰寫劇本的標竿<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web | author=Greg Kasavin | title=Final Fantasy IV Advance Review | date=2005-12-12 | url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/finalfantasyiv/review.html | publisher=CBS Interactive | accessdate=2011-08-06 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60kLqP44y?url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/finalfantasyiv/review.html | archivedate=2011-08-06 | language=en | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《最终幻想VII》被视作系列在产业中影响最大的作品<ref name="GT-FFRetrospectiveV">{{cite web| url = http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-v-final-fantasy/23449| title = Final Fantasy Retrospective Part V| publisher = GameTrailers| date = 2007-08-13| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090611163946/http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-v-final-fantasy/23449| archivedate = 2009-06-11| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>，并让主機平台的RPG在北美获得對大众市场的吸引力<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2006-08-29-dirge-of-cerberus_x.htm| title = 'Dirge of Cerberus' defies expectations, for better and worse| author = Alex Kraus| publisher = USA Today| date = 2006-08-30| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kM7Puao?url=http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2006-08-29-dirge-of-cerberus_x.htm| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

Final Fantasy系列一定程度影响著史克威尔的商业活动。電影《最终幻想：灵魂深处》的商业失败让艾尼克斯在与史克威尔的合并议案中犹豫不决<ref name="FFMovie-RPGamer" /><ref name="FF-Retro-1" />。1996年史克威尔發表將在索尼PlayStation平台推出独占的Final Fantasy遊戲，隔年作品上市後也一定程度幫助PS遊戲機取得了同世代機種中最大的市占率，這間接導致艾尼克斯隨後的[[勇者斗恶龙系列|勇者斗恶龙]]續作選擇了硬體銷量最高的PS平台，史克威尔此次決斷無疑是放棄了其与任天堂長久的合作关系<ref name="GS-FFHistory-Main" /><ref name="IGN-StateOfRPG" />；最终幻想游戏随后七年未在任天堂游戏机平台——特别是[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]——发行<ref name="UltimateHistory" /><ref name="GT-FFRetrospectiveV" />。评论认为，像最终幻想和勇者斗恶龙这种强力第三方作品，离开任天堂64转而登陆索尼PlayStation，是PlayStation在两个平台中更为成功的因素之一<ref name="GS-FFHistory-Main" /><ref name="IGN-StateOfRPG" /><ref name="IGN-N64week" />。2001年，使用光碟媒体的[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]发行，这引起史克威尔的注意。为了给该系统制作游戏，史克威尔建立[[空壳公司|空壳公司]][[The_Game_Designers_Studio|The Game Designers Studio]]并发行《[[最终幻想水晶编年史|最终幻想水晶编年史]]》，该作品后来发展为[[最终幻想水晶编年史系列|独立系列]]<ref name="GT-FFRetrospectiveXI" />。《最终幻想XI》不能在线取消订阅促使美国[[伊利诺斯州|伊利诺斯州]]立法，要求在线游戏服务商必须为州民提供订阅取消方式<ref name="GWR09-RPG">{{cite book| title = Guinness World Records 2009 Gamer's Edition| url = https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_x9q9| series= Guinness World Records| date = 2009-02-03| publisher= Guinness| isbn= 978-1-904994-45-9| pages= [https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_x9q9/page/174 174]–175| chapter= Record Breaking Games: Role-Playing Games|language=en}}</ref>。

随着最终幻想的普及，系列元素出现在动画、连续剧和[[網路漫畫|網路漫畫]]等各类流行文化中<ref>{{cite book| author = Timothy J. Craig | title = Japan Pop!: Inside the World of Japanese Popular Culture| url = https://archive.org/details/japanpopinsidew00crai | publisher = M.E. Sharpe| year = 2000| page = [https://archive.org/details/japanpopinsidew00crai/page/140 140]| isbn = 0-7656-0561-9|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2006/05/4078.ars| author = Ben Kuchera| title = Robot Chicken pokes fun at Final Fantasy| publisher = Ars Technica| date = 2006-05-23| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kMR9oYI?url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2006/05/4078.ars| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.vgcats.com/ffxi/| title = Adventure Log| publisher = VG Cats| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090418045027/http://www.vgcats.com/ffxi/| archivedate = 2009-04-18| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。系列音乐流入文化的各方各面。《最终幻想IV》的《爱之主题曲》选入[[日本教育|日本学龄儿童课程]]，并曾由管弦和金属乐团演奏<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-iii-final-fantasy/22905| title = Final Fantasy Retrospective Part III| date = 2007-07-30| publisher = GameTrailers| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090609180025/http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-iii-final-fantasy/22905| archivedate = 2009-06-09| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。2003年，植松伸夫加入[[黑魔导士|黑魔导士]]——一个独立于史克威尔，[[改编_(音乐)|改编]]最终幻想乐曲的摇滚乐团<ref>{{cite web| url = http://na.square-enix.com/uematsu/profile/index.html| title = Nobuo Uematsu's Profile| publisher = Square Enix| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kMjNtlD?url=http://na.square-enix.com/uematsu/profile/index.html| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.dogearrecords.com/tbm3/| title = The Black Mages-Darkness and Starlight| publisher = Dog Ear Records| language = ja| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kMsNifh?url=http://www.dogearrecords.com/tbm3/| archivedate = 2011-08-06| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会花样游泳比赛|2004年夏季奥运会花样游泳]]女子双人组铜牌得主{{le|艾莉森·巴托斯克|Alison Bartosik}}和{{le|安娜·科兹洛娃|Anna Kozlova}}的在常规赛中的伴奏音乐来自《最终幻想VIII》<ref name="GWR08-RPG" />。许多作品都會發行官方[[原聲音樂|原聲音樂]]。系列也发行了许多相关书籍，其中多为提供更深入的游戏信息與遊玩攻略。在日本，官方發行的系列书籍合称为[[Ultimania|Ultimania]]<ref>{{cite web| url = http://ps2.ign.com/articles/097/097559p1.html| title = Final Fantasy X Ultimania Guide| date = 2001-08-20| publisher = IGN Entertainment| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kN2rm0t?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/097/097559p1.html| archivedate = 2011-08-06| language = en| deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/gamebooks/ult/index.html| title = Square Enix Game Books Online| publisher = Square Enix| language = ja| accessdate = 2011-08-06| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/60kN5xRoI?url=http://www.square-enix.co.jp/magazine/gamebooks/ult/index.html| archivedate = 2011-08-06| deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

